Doc - You want venting, here's some venting. I told you before, I would never shove that shingle in you face, you have the right to be Barry Spatz on this site. I have never refered to your credentials to back up an argument with you and I never will. As far as I am concerned, you are just average Joe Schmuck!<br><br>
Secondly, I am a medic, always have been, always will be. You once threw out the crap about &quot;being the voice in your ear&quot;, well, I stand up for I believe is right, I stand up against tyrannical treatment, I stand up to bullies. In my life, I have had my damn ass kicked more than I can count, but, to borrow a phrase I so dearly enjoyed, a medic's gotta do what a medic gotta do.<br><br>
Next, about sounding like a damn racist, yes you do. I can deal with that and even convince myself that you are not, but the experience that I had this past weekend really jaded me. The same fucken arguments that you presented here, this very night, I had six parrallel debates with those who called themselves Vietnam veterans. But they were not as civil as you and I have been on site and I was on this stinking computer 18 hours a day Saturday and Sunday. <br><br>
Like I said, they tried to use the EXACT same arguments as you are trying, however, they did not leave out phrases like, &quot;that fucken slant-eyed bitch&quot; and that probably is the mellowest thrown out at me.  I was meat, raw damn meat for these folks, but I dealt with it cause thats the cost of putting up your address, and you fucken wonder why anyone, much less women, would hesitate to post those damn address?<br><br>
And the session you and I had this last weekend was a cakewalk compared to those six, but I tell you now that I don't give a rats ass how dragged down I get, I will always take you guys on if you are honest, forthwith and don't send anon hate crap. Fucken babies do that crap. Come on, do your best, do your worst, this mother fucken burnt out piece of shit is ready for all comers.<br><br>
And maybe I expect to much, but I got really fucken depress dealing with dormant racism on site and overt racism off site, so I put out four e-mails letting people, no, I let my fellow vets know that I felt like shit and guess what? No one was home. Do me a favor guys. Stop the cameraderie bullshit and promises about being there when needed. It didn't happen in 'Nam and it isn't happening here. I hate games; I hate lies!<br><br>
How's that for venting, DOC?
